#: getinvolved.html:13
msgid "Get Involved"
msgstr "Involucreu-vos-hi"

#: getinvolved.html:17
msgid "Thanks for Your Support"
msgstr "Gràcies per l'ajuda"

#: getinvolved.html:18
msgid ""
"<span name=\"distro-name\"></span> receives a great deal of support from its"
" community of users and we would like to thank each and every contributor "
"for participating. We are growing at a steady pace and our distribution is "
"getting better every day thanks to you."
msgstr ""
"<span name=\"distro-name\"></span> rep molt de suport de la comunitat "
"d'usuaris i volem donar les gràcies a cada un dels col·laboradors per "
"participar-hi. Estem creient a un ritme constant i la nostra distribució "
"cada dia és millor gràcies a tothom que hi participa."

#: getinvolved.html:19
msgid ""
"It is very easy to make a difference. Depending on your skill set, your "
"availability you can help <span name=\"distro-name\"></span> in one or more "
"of the following ways:"
msgstr ""
"És molt fàcil marcar la diferència. Segons les vostres habilitats, la vostra"
" disponibilitat pot ajudar <span name=\"distro-name\"> </span> en una o més "
"de les maneres següents:"

#: getinvolved.html:23
msgid "Support &amp; Promotion"
msgstr "Suport i promoció"

#: getinvolved.html:24
msgid "Spreading the word"
msgstr "Fer-ho córrer"

#: getinvolved.html:25
msgid ""
"If you like <span name=\"distro-name\"></span>, let people know. Blog, add "
"comments in forums and talk about it with your friends and the people around"
" you."
msgstr ""
"Si us agrada <span name=\"distro-name\"> </span>, feu que ho sàpiga la gent."
" Parleu-ne en blogs, afegiu comentaris en fòrums i parleu-ne amb els amics i"
" la gent que us envolta."

#: getinvolved.html:27
msgid "Joining the Community"
msgstr "Afegir-se a la comunitat"

#: getinvolved.html:28
msgid ""
"<span name=\"distro-name\"></span> isn't just an operating system, it's also"
" a dynamic community of people who enjoy, gather, and interact with a free "
"and open project. Whether it's by helping others sort through issues, by "
"making them feel welcome, or simply by meeting and talking to other <span "
"name=\"distro-name\"></span> users, we recommend you join the community and "
"participate in making <span name=\"distro-name\"></span> better."
msgstr ""
"No és només un sistema operatiu, també és una comunitat dinàmica de gent que"
" frueix, comparteix i interacciona amb un projecte lliure i obert. La gent "
"ajuda els altres a resoldre problemes, fent-los sentir benvinguts, o "
"simplement es troba i parla amb altres usuaris <span name=\"distro-"
"name\"></span>, us recomanem que us sumeu a la comunitat i hi participeu per"
" fer <span name=\"distro-name\"></span>millor."

#: getinvolved.html:30
msgid "Helping others"
msgstr "Ajudant la gent"

#: getinvolved.html:31
msgid ""
"If you have some spare time and you're willing to help other users with "
"technical problems, you should seriously consider reading the forums and/or "
"joining the community chat-room and helping other <span name=\"distro-"
"name\"></span> users solve the problems you know how to fix."
msgstr ""
"Si disposeu d'una mica de temps lliure i podeu ajudar altra gent a resoldre "
"els seus problemes tècnics, hauríeu de llegir als fòrums i/o unir-vos a les "
"converses de la comunitat i ajudar altres usuaris <span name=\"distro-"
"name\"></span> a resoldre els problemes dels quals en coneixeu la solució."

#: getinvolved.html:35
msgid "Project contributions"
msgstr "Contribucions al Projecte"

#: getinvolved.html:36
msgid "Bug reports"
msgstr "Informe d'errors"

#: getinvolved.html:37
msgid ""
"If you've noticed something that doesn't work properly while using <span "
"name=\"distro-name\"></span>, let us know. The problem you have discovered "
"is likely to affect others as well; The sooner we know about it, the sooner "
"we're able to fix it."
msgstr ""
"Si observeu que hi ha alguna cosa que no treballa correctament mentre "
"utilitzeu <span name=\"distro-name\"></span>, feu-nos-ho saber. Pot ser un "
"problema generalitzat; com més aviat sapiguem què passa, més aviat podrem "
"reparar-ho."

#: getinvolved.html:39
msgid "New ideas"
msgstr "Idees noves"

#: getinvolved.html:40
msgid ""
"The vast majority of improvements included in each release come from the "
"community. If there's something that you think is missing or that could be "
"done better, please tell us. Whether it's the inclusion of a missing "
"software application that should be part of a stock installation or if you "
"have any other ideas on how to make <span name=\"distro-name\"></span> "
"better, we're always interested in hearing them."
msgstr ""
"La gran majoria de millores que s'inclouen en cada lliurament successiu "
"provenen de la comunitat. Si penseu que cal cobrir alguna capacitat que s'ha"
" oblidat o que es podria millorar, si us plau, digueu-nos-ho. Ja sigui la "
"inclusió d'una aplicació oblidada que hauria de formar part del conjunt "
"instal·lat o qualsevol altra idea de com millorar <span name=\"distro-"
"name\"></span>, sempre estarem interessats de conèixer-les."

#: getinvolved.html:42
msgid "Artwork"
msgstr "Treball artístic"

#: getinvolved.html:43
msgid ""
"If you are talented in graphic design and willing to contribute to the "
"project, please send us your creations and artwork. Whether it's a simple "
"wallpaper, an icon set, a splash screen, or even a new logo, we're always "
"interested to hear from you about new artwork."
msgstr ""
"Si teniu habilitats per al disseny gràfic i desitgeu contribuir al project, "
"envieu-nos les vostres creacions i el treball gràfic. Des d'un fons de "
"pantalla a un grup d'icones, una pantalla d'inici, o fins i tot un logo nou,"
" sempre estem atents al que ens feu arribar."

#: getinvolved.html:45
msgid "Code"
msgstr "Codi"

#: getinvolved.html:46
msgid ""
"Most of our development is done in GTK+3, C++, Vala, Python and HTML5/CSS. "
"We also use Git for version control and .deb for packaging. If you're "
"comfortable with any of these technologies, don't hesitate to have a look at"
" the code. If you think you can improve our applications or write new ones "
"don't hesitate to suggest patches or to fork our git repositories."
msgstr ""
"La major part del nostre desenvolupament s'ha fet en GTK+3, C++, Vala, "
"Python i HTML5/CSS. També fem servir el sistema Git de control de versions i"
" empaquetats .deb. Si domineu qualsevol d'aquestes tecnologies, feu un cop "
"d'ull al codi. Si us sembla que podeu millorar les nostres aplicacions o "
"escriure'n de noves, suggeriu-nos les modificacions o derivacions als "
"repositoris git."

#: getinvolved.html:47
msgid ""
"Upstream to us is cinnamon-desktop. Created by Solus, they are looking for C "
"developers - so please help if you can."
msgstr ""
"L'escriptori Cinnamon és una prioritat nostra. Creat per Solus, els interessa "
"trobar programadors C - si podeu, ajudeu-los."

#: getinvolved.html:51
msgid ""
"It appears you are not connected to the Internet. Please check your "
"connection to access this content."
msgstr ""
"Sembla que no esteu connectat a Internet. Si us plau, comproveu la connexió "
"per accedir a aquest contingut."

#: getinvolved.html:52
msgid "Sorry, Welcome was unable to establish a connection."
msgstr "Ho sento, Welcome no ha pogut establir una connexió."

#: getinvolved.html:53
msgid "Retry"
msgstr "Torna-hi"

#: getinvolved.html:76
msgid "Cinnamon Desktop GitHub"
msgstr "GitHub de l'escriptori Cinnamon"

#: getinvolved.html:83
msgid ""
"Also, we have published a complete list of available opportunities on our "
"website. Please feel free to visit our website and find out in which way you"
" can contribute to our mission."
msgstr ""
"A més hem publicat una llista completa de les ofertes disponibles al nostre "
"lloc web. Si us plau, visiteu-lo i mireu si teniu la possiblitat de "
"contribuir amb la nostra misssió."

#: getinvolved.html:88
msgid "Opportunities"
msgstr "Oportunitats"
